  "original_title": "\u0d85\u0dba\u0dd2.\u0d91\u0db8\u0dca.\u0d91\u0dc6\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dc4\u0dad\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d89\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Requests an IMF certificate",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "In order to obtain approval from the Executive Board of the International Monetary Fund to extend an extended funding facility to Sri Lanka as Sri Lanka's debt has been determined to be unsustainable, the International Monetary Fund said in a statement that it needs sufficient assurances from creditors that Sri Lanka will restore debt sustainability.",
        "It is stated in the announcement that officials of the International Monetary Fund will visit Sri Lanka from the 24th to the 31st to discuss economic and financial reforms and policies with the Sri Lankan authorities.",
        "The IMF stated that the purpose of the visit was to make progress towards reaching a staff-level agreement to provide credit to Sri Lanka soon.",
        "The International Monetary Fund said that Masahiro Nozaki and Peter Brewer will lead the team of IMF officials visiting Sri Lanka."
      ],
